# Test Videos

This folder is excluded from the repository due to large file sizes (4K MP4).
Place your test video files here before running the tracker.

---

### 🚁 Test 1 — Drone Footage
**File:** `test_1.mp4`  
Top-down 4K drone clip of a silver car on a road. 280 frames at 24 fps, resolution 3840×2160.  
Used to evaluate tracker performance under uniform object texture and background corner competition.

---

### 📷 Test 2 — Surveillance Footage
**File:** `test_2.mp4`  
Oblique 4K surveillance clip of a car exiting frame-left. 529 frames at 30 fps, resolution 3840×2160.  
Used to evaluate tracker performance under exit-phase point degradation and velocity prediction.

---

> **Note:** Videos are not publicly shared. To test the tracker, use any 4K vehicle footage
> and set the correct path, `start_frame`, and `bbox` in `config.yaml`.
